bal-hunger-crisis" class="sf-depth-2">Global Hunger Crisis</a></li><li id="menu-97720-1" class="middle even sf-item-4 sf-depth-2 sf-no-children"><a href="/emergencies/global-refugee-crisis" class="sf-depth-2">Global Refugee Crisis</a></li><li id="menu-118954-1" class="middle odd sf-item-5 sf-depth-2 sf-no-children"><a href="/emergencies/syria-crisis" class="sf-depth-2">Syria Crisis</a></li><li id="menu-3112-1" class="last even sf-item-6 sf-depth-2 sf-no-children"><a href="/emergencies/women" class="sf-depth-2">Women &amp; Children</a></li></ol></li></ul></li><li id="menu-492-1" class="middle odd sf-item-3 sf-depth-1 sf-total-children-4 sf-parent-children-0 sf-single-children-4 menuparent"><a href="/our-impact" title="Our Impact" class="sf-depth-1 menuparent">Our Impact</a><ul class="sf-megamenu"><li class="sf-megamenu-wrapper middle odd sf-item-3 sf-depth-1 sf-total-children-4 sf-parent-children-0 sf-single-children-4 menuparent"><ol><li id="menu-136453-1" class="first odd sf-item-1 sf-depth-2 sf-no-children"><a href="/impact/stories" title="Our Stories" class="sf-depth-2">Our Stories</a></li><li id="menu-3109-1" class="middle even sf-item-2 sf-depth-2 sf-no-children"><a href="/impact/careknowshow" title="CARE Knows How" class="sf-depth-2">CARE Knows How</a></li><li id="menu-78637-1" class="middle odd sf-item-3 sf-depth-2 sf-no-children"><a href="/our-impact/joinmyvillage" title="" class="sf-depth-2">Join My Village</a></li><li id="menu-39079-1" class="last even sf-item-4 sf-depth-2 sf-no-children"><a href="/our-impact/usaid-technical-project-briefs" class="sf-depth-2">USAID Technical Project Briefs</a></li></ol></li></ul></li><li id="menu-493-1" class="middle even sf-item-4 sf-depth-1 sf-total-children-4 sf-parent-children-4 sf-single-children-0 menuparent"><a href="/get-involved" title="Get Involved" class="sf-depth-1 menuparent">Get Involved</a><ul class="sf-megamenu"><li class="sf-megamenu-wrapper middle even sf-item-4 sf-depth-1 sf-total-children-4 sf-parent-ch